<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Infratuzilma on RailTech</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/tags/infratuzilma/</link><description>Recent content in Infratuzilma on RailTech</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>uz</language><atom:link href="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/tags/infratuzilma/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Toshkent OTBM uchun diagnostika uskunalari</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/diagnostic-equipment/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/diagnostic-equipment/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Loyiha haqida
 &lt;div id="loyiha-haqida" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#loyiha-haqida" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2024-yilda «RailTech» Toshkent ochiq turdagi boshqaruv mexanizmi (OTBM) uchun zamonaviy diagnostika uskunalarini yetkazib berish loyihasini amalga oshirdi.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Vazifa
 &lt;div id="vazifa" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#vazifa" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vagonlarni ta&amp;rsquo;mirlash va texnik xizmat ko&amp;rsquo;rsatish sifatini oshirish maqsadida zamonaviy diagnostika uskunalarini yetkazib berish va joriy etish.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Amalga oshirilgan ishlar
 &lt;div id="amalga-oshirilgan-ishlar" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#amalga-oshirilgan-ishlar" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Korxona ehtiyojlarini tahlil qilish va texnik topshiriq ishlab chiqish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diagnostika uskunalarini tanlash va xorijdan yetkazib berish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uskunalarni o&amp;rsquo;rnatish va sozlash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Xodimlarni uskunalar bilan ishlash bo&amp;rsquo;yicha o&amp;rsquo;qitish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Texnik hujjatlarni o&amp;rsquo;zbek tiliga tarjima qilish va moslash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Natijalar
 &lt;div id="natijalar" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#natijalar" aria-label="Якорь"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yangi diagnostika uskunalari ta&amp;rsquo;mirlash sifatini sezilarli oshirdi va nosozliklarni aniqlash vaqtini qisqartirdi. Korxona xodimlari yangi uskunalar bilan ishlash bo&amp;rsquo;yicha to&amp;rsquo;liq o&amp;rsquo;qitildi.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/uz/projects/diagnostic-equipment/featured.jpg"/></item></channel></rss>